@minrk the difference comes down to `Instance.make_dynamic_default` and #315.

I should have linked to that issue before, because we could inherit from `Instance` instead of `MustBeInstance` if `Instance` traits with `allow_none=True` did not have a default value.

So whether we need `MustBeInstance` comes down to how we handle #315.

